  Android 12+ SplashScreen API (192dp inner safe-zone inside a 432dp viewport).
  Replaces the 4-shape Google-colored animated icon. Kept as a VectorDrawable so
  the existing `windowSplashScreenAnimatedIcon` attribute still loads it (Android
  treats a non-AnimatedVectorDrawable as a static icon with 0 ms animation).
-->
